PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Transport of ALLAN E. MAHER, of Dalhousie, New Brunswick, as a director of the board of directors of the Canada Ports Corporation to hold office during pleasure for a term of ten months, in the place of Raymond Landry, whose term has expired.
